Some Tweets from the now-deleted @FactCheckNig:backhand_index_pointing_down_medium-dark_skin_tone::backhand_index_pointing_down_medium-dark_skin_tone::backhand_index_pointing_down_medium-dark_skin_tone:

It’s true, there’s been a lot of false #EndSARS information and there IS a need to fact-check. However, there is NO room for pro-government actors pretending to be impartial INDEPENDENT fact-checkers. Please be transparent! :folded_hands_medium-dark_skin_tone: https://t.co/by0X7wmZCm
